by the orchard owners who will try to keep the pears safe,

754
00:25:08,294 --> 00:25:09,854
- Okay.
- you have to steal the pears.

755
00:25:11,264 --> 00:25:12,364
We have to run fast.

756
00:25:12,824 --> 00:25:15,464
Who are the orchard owners? Will it be an athlete like Kim Min Ji?

757
00:25:17,304 --> 00:25:18,603
Each stolen pear...

758
00:25:18,604 --> 00:25:21,333
will be converted to a dollar for your allowance.

759
00:25:21,334 --> 00:25:22,434
- A dollar?
- Per pear.

760
00:25:22,534 --> 00:25:24,244
I guess our chances aren't that bad.

761
00:25:24,404 --> 00:25:25,973
- If we can earn a dollar per pear, - Yes. A dollar.

762
00:25:25,974 --> 00:25:27,043
