- Yes?

818
00:27:02,904 --> 00:27:04,843
In the long jump...

819
00:27:04,844 --> 00:27:07,214
at the 2025 South Jeolla Province Student Sports Festival.

820
00:27:08,274 --> 00:27:09,313
(That's impressive.)

821
00:27:09,314 --> 00:27:10,343
That's incredible. How far did you jump?

822
00:27:10,344 --> 00:27:11,344
That's impressive.

823
00:27:11,345 --> 00:27:13,913
I jumped between 4.2m and 4.4m.

824
00:27:13,914 --> 00:27:14,983
- You jumped four meters?
- Yes.

825
00:27:14,984 --> 00:27:16,253
- Four meters?
- What? You only jumped once,

826
00:27:16,254 --> 00:27:17,694
- and you jumped four meters?
- Yes.

827
00:27:18,124 --> 00:27:19,953
- Is that even possible?
- What?

828
00:27:19,954 --> 00:27:21,924
Also, So Myung is...

829
00:27:22,454 --> 00:27:24,363
a track and field representative athlete...

830
00:27:24,364 --> 00:27:25,793
