852
00:28:03,294 --> 00:28:04,604
- This big?
- Exactly.

853
00:28:05,104 --> 00:28:06,264
Moon Se Yoon will run.

854
00:28:07,374 --> 00:28:09,094
(Are you saying that I'm the worst runner?)

855
00:28:09,404 --> 00:28:12,243
Someone might ask for proof if I say this,

856
00:28:12,244 --> 00:28:13,344
