857
00:28:13,844 --> 00:28:15,574
I was always the anchor leg in the relay.

858
00:28:16,044 --> 00:28:17,643
- Really?
- I'm being honest.

859
00:28:17,644 --> 00:28:19,913
We were given either a stamp or a ribbon.

860
00:28:19,914 --> 00:28:21,614
I always got the red ribbon.

861
00:28:21,914 --> 00:28:24,123
- When you're the anchor leg, - Right.

862
00:28:24,124 --> 00:28:25,923
You receive the baton as early as possible.

863
00:28:25,924 --> 00:28:26,993
I was the anchor leg.

864
00:28:26,994 --> 00:28:29,093
- I pick So Myung. You run.
- You go first.

865
00:28:29,094 --> 00:28:30,963
- You should do it.
- You go.

866
00:28:30,964 --> 00:28:32,123
- Come on.
- Seriously?

867
00:28:32,124 --> 00:28:33,224
On top of that...

868
00:28:33,394 --> 00:28:35,493
(That's how the legendary matchup is set.)

869
00:28:35,494 --> 00:28:37,063
- Now...
- You could be faster...

870
00:28:37,064 --> 00:28:39,333
during the 1st 30 meters since it's a short distance.

871
00:28:39,334 --> 00:28:40,873
You have to win no matter what.

872
00:28:40,874 --> 00:28:43,134
- So Myung.
- So Myung, you can do it.

873
00:28:43,504 --> 00:28:45,404
So Myung, you can do it.

874
00:28:45,774 --> 00:28:48,074
Do you have any siblings?

875
00:28:48,644 --> 00:28:50,313
- I have 2 older brothers.
- You have 2 older brothers?

876
00:28:50,314 --> 00:28:52,154
Do you run faster than middle school students?

877
00:28:52,584 --> 00:28:53,883
- A little bit.
- Seriously?

878
00:28:53,884 --> 00:28:54,884
Yes.

879
00:28:55,284 --> 00:28:56,413
(The rest of the players are huddled together.)

880
00:28:56,414 --> 00:28:57,423
- Which brand are your shoes?
- Hello.

881
00:28:57,424 --> 00:28:58,683
- Hi.
- Congratulations on your wedding.

882
00:28:58,684 --> 00:28:59,783
Thank you.

883
00:28:59,784 --> 00:29:01,053
(People still congratulate him on his wedding.)

884
00:29:01,054 --> 00:29:02,553
- You got married?
- He congratulated me on my wedding.

885
00:29:02,554 --> 00:29:03,693
(Yoon Seo congratulated me on my wedding.)

886
00:29:03,694 --> 00:29:05,094
- That's cute.
- "Congratulations?"

887
00:29:05,124 --> 00:29:07,393
- He has cute eyes.
- "Congratulations on your wedding."

888
00:29:07,394 --> 00:29:08,610
(A bright-eyed elementary school kid)

889
00:29:08,634 --> 00:29:10,864
Since you're an athlete, shall I take a step forward?

890
00:29:11,234 --> 00:29:12,304
- No.
- Is that so?

891
00:29:12,464 --> 00:29:14,104
She won't go easy on me.

892
00:29:14,704 --> 00:29:15,803
Se Yoon, show us.

893
00:29:15,804 --> 00:29:18,244
- Are you ready?
- They look nervous.

894
00:29:18,744 --> 00:29:19,774
Get ready,

895
00:29:20,514 --> 00:29:21,514
set...

896
00:29:22,274 --> 00:29:23,783
(127kg versus the province representative)

897
00:29:23,784 --> 00:29:24,784
Go!

898
00:29:25,584 --> 00:29:27,954
(Who will run faster?)

899
00:29:28,184 --> 00:29:29,184
Go!

900
00:29:30,154 --> 00:29:32,034
(Se Yoon is really running with all his might.)

901
00:29:32,484 --> 00:29:34,564
(On the other hand, So Myung is running peacefully.)

902
00:29:36,054 --> 00:29:37,264
(Laughing)

903
00:29:37,894 --> 00:29:40,434
(The gap widens as soon as they start.)

904
00:29:41,364 --> 00:29:44,264
(Without a twist, So Myung wins.)

905
00:29:44,664 --> 00:29:46,063
(Now you understand how good we are, right?)

906
00:29:46,064 --> 00:29:47,874
She runs really fast.

907
00:29:48,274 --> 00:29:50,103
So Myung, you're an amazing runner.

908
00:29:50,104 --> 00:29:52,174
I thought that I'd win by two seconds.

909
00:29:52,944 --> 00:29:54,474
- How springy...
- She ran very fast.

910
00:29:54,674 --> 00:29:56,174
Did you do your best?

911
00:29:56,714 --> 00:29:57,743
- Of course not.
- No.

912
00:29:57,744 --> 00:29:59,014
She ran half-heartedly.

913
00:29:59,384 --> 00:30:00,513
She didn't do her best.

914
00:30:00,514 --> 00:30:02,214
- We're in trouble.
- By the way, I...

915
00:30:02,654 --> 00:30:04,483
Under what rules will we play against them?

916
00:30:04,484 --> 00:30:05,853
All right, everyone.

917
00:30:05,854 --> 00:30:08,924
A while ago, I told you that you'd steal the pears.

918
00:30:09,294 --> 00:30:12,124
You will have to steal water balloon pears.

919
