921
00:30:17,534 --> 00:30:19,664
Answer the question that's on top of the box.

922
00:30:19,804 --> 00:30:22,604
Guess the lock combination in order to open the box.

923
00:30:23,234 --> 00:30:24,404
That sounds difficult.

924
00:30:24,604 --> 00:30:27,414
Each box has a different type of question and number of pears.

925
00:30:27,714 --> 00:30:30,984
The orchard owners will start 15 seconds...

926
00:30:31,284 --> 00:30:34,014
