929
00:30:38,884 --> 00:30:41,054
you'll lose your chance.

930
00:30:41,254 --> 00:30:42,423
We must answer the question fast.

931
00:30:42,424 --> 00:30:45,264
(They must answer fast and run away quickly.)

932
00:30:45,864 --> 00:30:48,164
Did the director or your coach say,

933
00:30:48,664 --> 00:30:52,163
