934
00:30:52,164 --> 00:30:53,873
Did they threaten you?

935
00:30:53,874 --> 00:30:55,074
- No.
- No, they didn't.

936
00:30:55,174 --> 00:30:56,303
They told us not to get hurt.

937
00:30:56,304 --> 00:30:57,843
- That's right.
- Exactly.

938
00:30:57,844 --> 00:30:58,903
It's important not to get hurt,

939
00:30:58,904 --> 00:30:59,973
so play slowly.

940
00:30:59,974 --> 00:31:00,974
- Right.
- Okay.

941
00:31:00,975 --> 00:31:02,473
- That's the right mindset.
- You must do it slowly.

942
00:31:02,474 --> 00:31:04,114
This isn't a competition. Take your time.

943
00:31:04,244 --> 00:31:09,014
(Warming up to avoid injuries)

944
00:31:09,414 --> 00:31:11,584
By the way, who was it?

945
00:31:12,154 --> 00:31:14,423
Tae Young's dad and Joon are the same age.

946
00:31:14,424 --> 00:31:15,493
- Really?
- His mom and I are the same age.

947
00:31:15,494 --> 00:31:16,893
His mom is the same age as DinDin.

948
00:31:16,894 --> 00:31:19,093
(A race against kids who are young enough to be their son)

949
00:31:19,094 --> 00:31:20,934
Maybe his grandfather is the same age as you.

950
00:31:21,094 --> 00:31:22,533
That's what I heard.

951
00:31:22,534 --> 00:31:24,580
(It's possible if he got married to his first love.)

952
00:31:24,604 --> 00:31:25,703
(The track and field athletes start to warm up.)

953
00:31:25,704 --> 00:31:26,704
