954
00:31:26,705 --> 00:31:27,974
Get a grip.

955
00:31:29,274 --> 00:31:30,803
I'll catch them right away.

956
00:31:30,804 --> 00:31:32,244
- Get ready.
- We can do it.

957
00:31:33,374 --> 00:31:34,844
Why are they so motivated?

958
00:31:35,144 --> 00:31:37,044
- He's so fast. Who is that?
- The race...

959
00:31:38,144 --> 00:31:39,244
I bet we'll lose.

960
00:31:40,044 --> 00:31:41,483
We're doomed if we don't know the answer.

961
00:31:41,484 --> 00:31:42,754
We'll get number one at least.

962
00:31:42,884 --> 00:31:43,953
Go to the very back.

963
00:31:43,954 --> 00:31:45,123
- We'll know when we go.
- If the question is hard,

964
00:31:45,124 --> 00:31:47,254
